{"word":"G2345 - θιγγάνω - thingánō - thing-gan'-o - Handle","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">θιγγάνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">thingánō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">thing-gan'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Handle</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - ருசிபார், தொடு"},{"paragraph":"to touch, handle"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>A prolonged form of an obsolete primary word <b>&#x03B8;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03B3;&#x03C9;</b> <b>thigo&#x0304;</b> (to <i>finger</i>); to <i>manipulate</i>, that is, <i>have to do with</i>; by implication to <i>injure:</i> - handle, touch.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}